  "text": "What we are to imagine in the internalization fantasy is something like a patient with multiple personality disorder. One personality, Searle, is uent in English (both written and spoken), doesn't know a word of Chinese, and is otherwise perfectly normal (except that he has the calculative powers of a mega idiot savant). The other ostensible personality -let's call him Hao -is uent in Chinese (though only writ-7 Syntax is not the same as, nor by itself is it sucient for, semantics, [CITATION_1] ].",
